      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 📬 Phase 1: The Smart Organizer\n**Goal: Categorize incoming mail instantly to keep the Inbox at Zero.**\n\nThe Smart Organizer is a high-performance automation designed to act as a \"Digital Gatekeeper.\" By leveraging Groq’s LPU Inference Engine and Llama 3.1, this workflow analyzes the intent of every incoming email in real-time, categorizes it, and clears the primary inbox—ensuring you only see what truly matters.\n\n* ⚡ **Instant Sorting:** \nWorks in the background the moment an email hits your inbox—no waiting.\n\n* 🧠 **Intelligent Labeling:** \nDynamically sorts emails into the following buckets:\n  - Personal, Learning & Newsletters, Socials, Receipts, Promotions, Login Alerts, and OTP/Codes.\n\n*  🧹 **Automatic Clean-up:** \nOnce it puts a label on an email, it moves it out of your main Inbox. This keeps your main view clean and distraction-free.\n\n* 🛠️ **Reliable Design:** Built as a separate \"worker\" so it stays fast and never misses an email..",
